data.description: Sellers offering $6,000.00 incentive to be used as needed by Buyers (closing cost? Repairs?). This kind of home doesn't come up often! Lots of room totaling 2,016 square feet on .41 acres with a detached garage/workshop. The all brick main home features 3 bedrooms/2 baths with granite countertops and lots of storage in the kitchen. An additional space has been added to the home which could be used as an In-law suite or even an attached rental to bring in extra income. Located in the city of Watertown close to shops, stores, and much more. *see the floor plan/measurements and photos below.
